txt.en: There is much to be done in the maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk.
Enter the maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk
The Orcs down here are well stocked with enough supplies for an entire army. You take it upon yourself to destroy some of these supplies in order to hinder the vile efforts of the armies of Mordor.
The maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should destroy Orc supplies scattered around the caverns.
The maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should destroy Orc supplies scattered around the caverns.
You have destroyed many of the Orc supplies within the maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk. This should lessen the effectiveness of the Orcs camped down here.
